            "size": 1374,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01LQf8DQqpzuDgPqdzWWrmFA\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nNow, let me generate the keywords for your campaign:\\n\\nI've suggested a few keywords your audience is likely searching for when your ad appears. How do these sound to you?\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"keywords\\\": [\\n    \\\"meeting scheduling tool\\\",\\n    \\\"calendar coordination software\\\",\\n    \\\"find meeting time across time zones\\\",\\n    \\\"team scheduling app\\\",\\n    \\\"automated meeting scheduler\\\",\\n    \\\"distributed team scheduling\\\",\\n    \\\"best scheduling tool for remote teams\\\",\\n    \\\"meeting scheduler for global teams\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nThese keywords target:\\n- **High-intent transactional** (keywords 1, 2, 4, 5, 7, 8): People actively searching for scheduling solutions\\n- **Problem-focused** (keyword 3): Teams struggling with timezone coordination\\n- **Awareness & comparison** (keyword 6): Broader searches from teams evaluating options\\n\\nWould you like me to adjust any of these, or shall we move forward with refining the headlines and descriptions?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3035,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":225,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
