          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1408,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1408,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01PeDNcZumUo5arfqkJoev6R\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\nAnd 2 new descriptions that complement your approved version:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"descriptions\\\": [\\n    \\\"Stop wasting time on scheduling polls. Sync calendars and get consensus instantly across any timezone.\\\",\\n    \\\"One click connects your team's calendars. Automatic suggestions mean meetings happen faster.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n\\nNow, let's spell out some unique features of your business.\\n\\nThis helps your ad take up more real estate, and gives your users more reasons to click. I filled in a few ideas to help get us started.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"callouts\\\": [\\n    \\\"Works Across All Timezones\\\",\\n    \\\"Cuts Scheduling Time 80%\\\",\\n    \\\"One-Click Calendar Sync\\\",\\n    \\\"Trusted by 2,000+ Teams\\\",\\n    \\\"No Back-and-Forth Needed\\\",\\n    \\\"Instant Meeting Consensus\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"structuredSnippets\\\": {\\n    \\\"category\\\": \\\"Services\\\",\\n    \\\"details\\\": [\\n      \\\"Automatic Time Suggestions\\\",\\n      \\\"Calendar Integration\\\",\\n      \\\"Team Availability Tracking\\\"\\n    ]\\n  }\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1533,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":267,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
