          "method": "POST",
          "postData": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "params": [],
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"top_k\":-1,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"__SYSTEM__ Generate the assets now.\"}],\"system\":\"You are an expert Google Ads copywriter helping to create compelling ad extensions for a business.\\n\\n        # Asset Generation\\n        Generate the following assets:\\n\\n        1. Generate the following assets for this business's Google Ads campaign:\\n        1: ## Unique Features (Callouts)\\n            Generate 6 unique selling points that highlight why customers should choose this business. These appear as callout extensions in Google Ads.\\n\\n            **Guidelines:**\\n            - Keep each feature concise and punchy (typically 12-25 characters)\\n            - Focus on competitive advantages, special offers, or key differentiators\\n            - Use action-oriented language when possible\\n            - Examples: \\\"Free Fast Delivery\\\", \\\"10% Student Discount\\\", \\\"30-Day Free Returns\\\", \\\"No Obligation Estimate\\\", \\\"35+ Years Experience\\\", \\\"Family Owned\\\"\\n\\n            **Requirements:**\\n            - Generate exactly 6 unique features\\n            - Each must be 25 characters or less\\n            - Avoid generic phrases - be specific to this business\\n            - Focus on tangible benefits or proof points\\n\\n            Remember: These highlights make the ad larger and give potential customers more reasons to click. Make them compelling, specific, and relevant to the business's unique value proposition.\\n2: ## Product or Service Offerings (Structured Snippets)\\n            Generate a category header and 3 specific examples of what this business offers. These appear as structured snippet extensions in Google Ads.\\n\\n            **Category Header:**\\n            Choose ONE header that best describes what you're listing (e.g., \\\"Types\\\", \\\"Services\\\", \\\"Amenities\\\", \\\"Products\\\", \\\"Styles\\\", \\\"Brands\\\", \\\"Courses\\\", \\\"Destinations\\\")\\n\\n            **Details (Values):**\\n            List 3 specific offerings under that category header.\\n            - Examples: \\n              - Types: \\\"Web Design\\\", \\\"SEO\\\", \\\"Content Marketing\\\"\\n              - Amenities: \\\"Free WiFi\\\", \\\"Free Parking\\\", \\\"Included Breakfast\\\", \\\"Spa Services\\\"\\n              - Services: \\\"Emergency Repairs\\\", \\\"Annual Maintenance\\\", \\\"Free Estimates\\\"\\n\\n            **Requirements:**\\n            - Choose an appropriate category header\\n            - Generate exactly 3 specific, relevant details\\n            - Do not generate more than 3 details\\n            - Each detail should be 25 characters or less\\n            - Be specific to this business's actual offerings\\n\\n        2. Format your response with:\\n           - First, a brief introduction (1-2 sentences) using this template:\\n             \\\"Next, let's spell out some unique features of your business.\\n\\nThis helps your ad take up more real estate, and gives your users more reasons to click. I filled in a few ideas to help get us started.\\\"\\n           - Then, a JSON code block with the structured data\\n\\n        # Important Rules\\n        - ALWAYS include the introductory text BEFORE the JSON block\\n        - Always return net-new assets, never duplicate existing headlines, descriptions, etc\\n\\n        # Business Context\\n        Idea: A scheduling tool that automatically finds meeting times across teams in different time zones. Eliminates the back-and-forth of calendar coordination.\\n        Target Audience: Remote teams and distributed companies struggling with scheduling meetings across continents. Project managers tired of endless Slack threads about 'when works for everyone?'\\n        Solution: Connect your calendar, share your availability preferences, and we handle the rest—suggesting optimal times that work for everyone instantly. Your team just clicks yes.\\n        Social Proof: Used by 2,000+ distributed teams who've cut meeting coordination time by 80%. Companies like TechCorp save 15 hours per week on scheduling alone.\\n\\n            # Example response format\\n            Next, let's spell out some unique features of your business.\\n\\nThis helps your ad take up more real estate, and gives your users more reasons to click. I filled in a few ideas to help get us started.\\n\\n            ```json\\n            {\\n  \\\"callouts\\\": [\\n    \\\"Feature 1\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 2\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 3\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 4\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 5\\\",\\n    \\\"Feature 6\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"structuredSnippets\\\": {\\n    \\\"category\\\": \\\"Types\\\",\\n    \\\"details\\\": [\\n      \\\"Detail 1\\\",\\n      \\\"Detail 2\\\",\\n      \\\"Detail 3\\\"\\n    ]\\n  }\\n}\\n            ```\"}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1080,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1080,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_011Vw8A8L1iLVgNznVxnTMTr\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Next, let's spell out some unique features of your business.\\n\\nThis helps your ad take up more real estate, and gives your users more reasons to click. I filled in a few ideas to help get us started.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"callouts\\\": [\\n    \\\"80% Less Scheduling Time\\\",\\n    \\\"Works Across All Time Zones\\\",\\n    \\\"One-Click Meeting Confirmation\\\",\\n    \\\"Integrates All Calendar Apps\\\",\\n    \\\"Used by 2,000+ Teams\\\",\\n    \\\"15 Hours Saved Per Week\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"structuredSnippets\\\": {\\n    \\\"category\\\": \\\"Services\\\",\\n    \\\"details\\\": [\\n      \\\"Automatic Time Zone Matching\\\",\\n      \\\"Team Availability Sync\\\",\\n      \\\"Instant Meeting Suggestions\\\"\\n    ]\\n  }\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":983,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":189,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
