            "size": 1434,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01JFqeomxvM6hgpu7mGHL78D\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"descriptions\\\": [\\n    \\\"No more 'does Tuesday work?' loops. Sync calendars across time zones and get instant suggestions everyone can attend.\\\",\\n    \\\"Distributed teams waste hours on scheduling. We automate it. See why 2,000+ teams switched.\\\",\\n    \\\"Your calendar. Their calendar. One tool. Meetings scheduled in seconds, not days.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\nNow, let's spell out some unique features of your business.\\n\\nThis helps your ad take up more real estate, and gives your users more reasons to click. I filled in a few ideas to help get us started.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"callouts\\\": [\\n    \\\"Works Across Time Zones\\\",\\n    \\\"Syncs All Calendar Apps\\\",\\n    \\\"Instant Time Suggestions\\\",\\n    \\\"80% Less Coordination\\\",\\n    \\\"Free Trial, No Credit Card\\\",\\n    \\\"2,000+ Teams Trust Us\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"structuredSnippets\\\": {\\n    \\\"category\\\": \\\"Features\\\",\\n    \\\"details\\\": [\\n      \\\"Automatic Calendar Sync\\\",\\n      \\\"Smart Availability Matching\\\",\\n      \\\"One-Click Scheduling\\\"\\n    ]\\n  }\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1767,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":277,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
